<p>
	Backflow Incense Cones when they are burned, the smoke flows down the incense tower like a waterfall, creating an unusual and beautiful effect. Perfect for anyone interested in creating a exotic and eye catching display in their home. These cones come in assorted colours and have only a subtle incense aroma.<br />
	These cones are only for use with Backflow Incense Burners.&nbsp;Backflow Incense can damage varnished surfaces, always use on a mat. To be used indoors and with no drafts for best effects.&nbsp;</p>
